defaultLocal authorities have a role, alongside an array of other partners, to support schools throughout their improvement journey. This involves identifying and 
defaultacting upon early warning signs that might, for example, suggest that educational standards are slipping.
default Councils’ ability to track individual pupil data 
defaultin real time, over a period of time, is important to spotting warning signs. Local authorities ought 
